The .out files in this directory are output files generated by ORCA
(https://orcaforum.kofo.mpg.de/), a quantum chemistry program developed at the
Max Planck Institute for Coal Research.

ORCA is proprietary software distributed free of charge for academic use under
its own license terms.  These files are included here solely as test fixtures
for the parser test suite and are NOT covered by the GPL-3.0 license that
governs the source code of this project.

To regenerate these files you need your own ORCA installation and licence.
